title: Kendall Jenner Is Back to Brunette and Wearing a Latex Floral Gown at the 2019 Emmys
text:
Photo credit: Alberto E. Rodriguez - Getty Images More

From ELLE

Kendall Jenner is on presenter duty tonight at the 2019 Emmy Awards with her sisters Kylie Jenner and Kim Kardashian. How did the model dress for the occasion? She went all out, wearing black floral dress. She also gave up her blonde hair: Jenner is a brunette again and had her hair up in a bun.

Photo credit: Alberto E. Rodriguez - Getty Images More

Photo credit: Alberto E. Rodriguez - Getty Images More

This is Jenner's very first time at the Emmys. The last awards show she unexpectedly attended was the 2018 Golden Globes. She wore a black Giambattista Valli dress there.
description: The blonde hair lasted less than a week.
